.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm atf-python
library was introduced to complement FreeBSD's Automated Testing Framework (ATF), providing extensive support for modern network features, such as IPv6, virtual networks (VNET), and routing socket management through a Pythonic interface.
.Sh AUTHORS
The
.Nm atf-python
library and related testing infrastructure were developed by the FreeBSD community and various contributors.
